readme:
Service Usage

This service retrieves a selected client's biometric enrolment(s) and match results.
These include internal, NAIFIS and FCC match results and associated metadata for foreign business service summaries.

Service Behaviour

CSP captures the required data and sends to BAMS to consume using SV398.
BAMS then sends data using SV540 to CDH
CDH then sends data using SV563 to CSP for display.
